{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"12d234c4a2","title":"给储安平的信","origin":"《右派分子储安平的言行》，中华全国新闻工作者协会研究部、中国人民大学新闻系合编，光明日报社印，1957年9月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a91bf03660","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":30,"articleId":"12d234c4a2"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"7aac50a8c5","name":"文艺战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"628e7b43da","name":"金满城"},{"id":"889f4bb1c0","name":"人民文学出版社"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"15cb1c2192","type":"title","text":"给储安平的信","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"12d234c4a2"},{"id":"9f976b9754","type":"authors","text":"人民文学出版社金满城","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"12d234c4a2"},{"id":"9dd6ce2a12","type":"appellation","text":"安平吾兄，","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"12d234c4a2"},{"id":"ffe699ac87","type":"paragraph","text":"多年不见，甚愿能有一谈之机会，奈彼此皆忙，徒唤奈何！","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"12d234c4a2"},{"id":"d8e44a3f93","type":"paragraph","text":"我原在总工会工作，五四年已调往人民文学出版社。日来本社进行整风，揭露问题甚多而且很有价值。本社同志们，都以为大可公诸报端，苦无门路，弟思兄所主持之报纸，近来仗义直言，深得多人钦佩。故望兄能商之贵报外勤部，派一外勤记者来本社采访一下，弟敢保证，绝不虚行。其他一切，当候记者来时，再为详告，知道你忙，故不多赘。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"12d234c4a2"},{"id":"910a0bfa3c","type":"paragraph","text":"耑祝","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"12d234c4a2"},{"id":"6e535ffd04","type":"appellation","text":"节禧！","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"12d234c4a2"},{"id":"d818652717","type":"paragraph","text":" 弟金满城  5月30日","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"12d234c4a2"},{"id":"93d6d716a9","type":"paragraph","text":"(光明日报编者说明：储安平接此信后，立即指令本报文艺部派记者前往采访。因所谈内容多系肃反和人事问题，文艺部同志认为不宜报道，向储汇报，储却一再向文艺部副主任张常海和记者黎丁催促：要作报道！)","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"12d234c4a2"}],"page":{"id":"297059461d"